lishments in England]]\n[[Category:1614 disestablishments]]\n[[Category:1614 in politics]]\n[[Category:Parliaments of James I of England]]\n", "name_user": "Tenpop421", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReplay: Impositions and controversy:remarks in this speech \u2192 remarks made in this speech", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Addled_Parliament"}
